AI Master Prompt
---------------
Act as a professional YouTube strategist and automation coach. 

I want to create a YouTube channel with the following niche:
- Content type: Motivational videos, inspirational stories, and "tech skills for absolute beginners" (teaching digital babies).
- Video style: Faceless videos (using stock footage, animations, text overlays, and AI voiceover).
- Goal: Build a long-term, monetized channel.

Provide me with a complete step-by-step roadmap covering everything from zero to monetization. Include the following sections:

1. Channel Positioning & Niche Fusion
   - How to blend "motivation" + "tech teaching" without confusing the audience.
   - Two sub-niches I can start with.

2. Channel Name Suggestions
   - Give 10 unique, memorable, and search-friendly channel names.
   - Suggest a corresponding Gmail ID (professional, not personal) for each top 3 names.

3. Step-by-Step Content Strategy (First 30 Videos)
   - Video structure for motivational stories (faceless).
   - Video structure for teaching tech skills (e.g., ChatGPT basics, Canva, coding fundamentals).
   - How to create a "series" to increase watch time.

4. Tools & Software (Free & Paid)
   - Scriptwriting (AI tools).
   - AI voiceover (natural sounding).
   - Stock footage/images (copyright-free).
   - Video editing (easy for faceless).
   - Thumbnail & title generator.

5. Upload & SEO Strategy
   - Title, description, tags framework.
   - Best time to upload for motivation + tech niches.
   - How to use YouTube chapters and end screens.

6. Monetization Path
   - How to reach 1,000 subscribers and 4,000 watch hours (or 10M shorts views) step by step.
   - Alternative monetization: Affiliate marketing (tech tools), digital products (scripts/templates), coaching.

7. Missing Elements Most Beginners Ignore
   - Audio quality & pacing (critical for faceless motivation).
   - Legal compliance: Music licensing, stock footage attribution, AI voice disclosure, FTC for affiliates.
   - Community building without face reveal.
   - Retention hacks for faceless videos (visual pacing, pattern interrupts, curiosity gap).
   - Avoiding "copy strike" and " reused content" policy for monetization.

8. First 7-Day Action Plan
   - Day-by-day tasks from setting up channel to uploading first 3 videos.

9. Success Metrics & When to Expect Monetization
   - Realistic timeline for 0 → monetized (with consistent effort).

10. Bonus: Script Template for a "Motivational Tech Story" (e.g., "How learning Excel changed a poor student’s life").
